Ansible,Advanced,Which class is required for custom Python modules to handle args and return structured JSON?,AnsibleModule,ActionBase,ModuleUtils,BasicModule,A,AnsibleModule from ansible.module_utils.basic provides argument parsing, fail_json/exit_json and common helpers.,https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/dev_guide/developing_modules_general.html,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+custom+module+python,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+hindi,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+kannada,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+tamil,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+telugu
Ansible,Advanced,What is the bare-minimum JSON key every Ansible module (any language) must return?,changed,failed,rc,msg,A,Every module must return at least {"changed": boolean}, optionally with "failed".,https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/dev_guide/developing_modules_general.html#return-values,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+custom+module,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+hindi,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+kannada,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+tamil,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+telugu
Ansible,Advanced,Where should custom callback plugins be placed for automatic discovery?,callback_plugins/ folder in project,plugins/callback/,library/callbacks/,ansible.cfg plugins section,A,Ansible automatically loads callbacks from callback_plugins/ in role/project/collection.,https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/plugins/callback.html,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+callback+plugin+development,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+hindi,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+kannada,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+tamil,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+telugu
Ansible,Advanced,Which base class should modern inventory plugins inherit from?,BaseInventoryPlugin,InventoryModule,BasePlugin,InventoryBase,A,Since Ansible 2.4+, inventory plugins inherit from ansible.plugins.inventory.BaseInventoryPlugin.,https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/plugins/inventory.html,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+inventory+plugin,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+hindi,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+kannada,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+tamil,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+telugu
Ansible,Advanced,What mechanism allows sharing Python code between multiple custom modules?,ansible.module_utils.*,Copy-paste code,ansible.utils library,lookup plugins,A,module_utils is the official way to share helpers across modules without duplication.,https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/dev_guide/developing_module_utilities.html,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+module_utils,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+hindi,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+kannada,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+tamil,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+telugu
Ansible,Advanced,Which ansible.cfg setting dramatically reduces SSH round-trips?,pipelining = True,control_persist = 30m,forks = 50,ssh_args = -C -o Compression=yes,A,pipelining executes many commands in one SSH session (requires no requiretty on sudoers).,https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/reference_appendices/config.html#pipelining,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+pipelining,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+hindi,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+kannada,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+tamil,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+telugu
Ansible,Advanced,What is the best combination to speed up Ansible on 1000+ nodes?,pipelining + redis fact caching + forks=100 + gather_subset=!all,A,These four reduce SSH, disk I/O, network and fact-gathering overhead the most.,https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/playbook_guide/playbooks_performance.html,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+performance+tuning,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+hindi,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+kannada,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+tamil,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+telugu
Ansible,Advanced,Which fact gathering strategy is optimal when you need only network facts?,gather_subset = network,gather_subset = minimal + set_fact,gather_facts: smart,gather_subset = !all,network,A,Explicit subset = network gathers only networking-related facts quickly.,https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/playbook_guide/playbooks_vars_facts.html#fact-subsets,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+gather_subset,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+hindi,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+kannada,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+tamil,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+telugu
Ansible,Advanced,What does async: 7200 + poll: 0 achieve?,Runs task for up to 2 hours in background, no waiting,Waits 2 hours for task,Poll every 7200 seconds,Disables task,A,poll: 0 + high async = classic fire-and-forget for very long jobs.,https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/playbook_guide/playbooks_async.html,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+async+fire+and+forget,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+hindi,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+kannada,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+tamil,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+telugu
Ansible,Advanced,How do you monitor a fire-and-forget async task later?,async_status module with registered job_id,wait_for module,job_status module,async_poll module,A,async_status polls the job using the async job identifier from register.,https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/collections/ansible/builtin/async_status_module.html,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+async_status,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+hindi,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+kannada,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+tamil,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+telugu
Ansible,Advanced,What is the safest way to do a rolling update on 500 servers with max 50 at a time?,serial: 50,serial: 10%,throttle: 50,strategy: free + serial: 50,A,serial: 50 processes exactly 50 hosts per batch — predictable and safe.,https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/playbook_guide/playbooks_strategies.html#rolling-updates,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+rolling+update,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+hindi,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+kannada,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+tamil,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+telugu
Ansible,Advanced,Which option aborts entire play on first failure anywhere?,any_errors_fatal: true,max_fail_percentage: 0,ignore_unreachable: false,rescue: abort,A,any_errors_fatal stops everything when any single host fails a task.,https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/playbook_guide/playbooks_error_handling.html,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+any_errors_fatal,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+hindi,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+kannada,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+tamil,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+telugu
Ansible,Advanced,Which when: condition safely checks two variables are both defined and non-empty?,when: var1 is defined and var1 | length > 0 and var2 is defined and var2 | length > 0,when: var1 and var2,when: var1 is truthy and var2 is truthy,when: var1 | default('') and var2 | default(''),A,Explicit defined + length check prevents errors and false positives.,https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/playbook_guide/playbooks_conditionals.html,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+complex+when,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+hindi,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+kannada,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+tamil,https://youtube.com/results?search_query=ansible+telugu
